        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>hf_stm32_temp_convert_fn</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>User-supplied function to convert a raw ADC count to Celsius. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For the STM32 internal sensor the typical formula is: T(°C) = ((V_SENSE – V_25) / Avg_Slope) + 25 but calibration constants differ per family (see RM).</para>
<para>For external NTC / PTC / thermocouple channels the user provides their own linearisation function. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
